oldentry: Popular explanation: putting ash in an ashtray.
verblex: 1. To flick the ash off the end of a cigarette or cigar by tapping your finger on it, usually into an ashtray. English = ash.
nomlex: 1. A small dish in which people can put the ash from their cigarettes and cigars. English = ashtray.
2. The grey or back powdery substance that is left after a cigarette or cigar is burnt. English = ash.
